transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Ji Punnu ji bataye.
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Hello awaz aa raha hai na?
Executive: Haan awaz aa raha hai sir aapka. Ji ji sir bole.
Customer: Sir aapke yahan se koi Mr. Prince karke mere ko call kar raha hai.
Executive: Kaun kaun?
Customer: Koi Mr. Prince Yadav ya aisa kuch naam hai wo bol raha hai mera catalog down hai do hafte se.
Executive: Achcha sir ye sir number aapne jo call kiya sir abhi kahan se call kiya app se call kiya aap?
Customer: Maine to app se hi call kiya tha aapko lekin mujhe jo call aaya tha na wo ek alag mobile number se aaya tha.
Executive: Ji ji sir wo main hi baat kar raha hun.
Executive: Isse kya hota hai ki yahan se kabhi kabhi call mobile number se chali jati hai kabhi kabhi virtual number se call chali jati hai isliye main hi Prince Choudhary baat kar raha hun sir. Theek hai sir aapko believe nahi ho raha tha to aapne phone disconnect kar diya tha us time aapne.
Customer: Aur ticket yahan se. Mera catalog to dikha raha hai mujhe.
Executive: Main aap main aapko na aap na ek minute main aapko kaise aapko main ek link bheju aapko video meet aap dekhenge sir dikhau main aapko.
Customer: Nahi nahi usme rates nahi dala hua hai wo theek hai.
Customer: Mujhe inquiries aa rahi hai sir.
Executive: Ji ji sir wahi sir aap main dekh raha hun sir aap kafi active hai sir aap aap mujhe active dikh rahe hai sir aap.
Customer: Haan wahi mujhe inquiries aa rahi hai rehne do jaisa hai waisa koi tension mat karo theek hai. Nahi nahi nahi nahi main tension nahi kar raha hun actually kya hota hai na aapko sir inquiry aa rahi hai business milna achchi baat hai sir but sir mera jo kaam hota hai sir main ki maniye ki main main daily check karta rehta hun ki kisi bhi client ka catalog isko down na ho kabhi jo product hai.
Customer: Ek kaam karo na sir aap kya wo Mr. Deepak hai na koi?
Executive: Deepak
Customer: Mr. Deepak wo hamesha coordination me to wo Deepak hi hota hai mere paas.
Executive: Nahi sir ye to case mere paas assign hui hai kuch time ke baad se main Deepak ko to nahi janta hun sir.
Customer: Nahi koi Deepak hi tha mera account manager Mr. Deepak karke koi the.
Executive: Deepak nahi nahi aap jaise kya hai na case mere paas assign ho gayi hai to mujhe nahi pata sir ki matlab Deepak kaun hai main hi aapke account manager hun jo maine iske pehle call kara aapko theek hai.
Customer: Nahi nahi sir koi Mr. Deepak tha mere ko barabar se yaad hai.
Executive: Sir ho sakta hai sir koi hoga Deepak theek hai but abhi mujhe nahi pata hai ki Deepak kaun aapke account manager the theek hai sir kyunki case mere paas assign ji case mere paas assign ho gaya sir agar aap free hai sir kuch time tak ek dekhiye abhi ticket bhi open ho gayi aapne jo call abhi kiya tha na abhi main aapse baat kar raha tha abhi to wo call disconnect ho gayi to wo ticket automatic ticket raise ho jata hai sir.
Customer: Nahi theek hai rehne do abhi main sirf kal ya parso main aapko call karta hun. Haan to sir aap na mere number ko save jo mera number tha na wo jo maine call kiya tha 995 karke tha wo wo na number aap mera save kar lijiyega ki kabhi aapko main call karun to kabhi aapko matlab misunderstanding na ho ki koi aur call kiya hai theek hai sir.
Customer: Theek hai sir okay. Ji aur main ek ticket abhi close karunga sir ye to aapke paas whatsapp pe ek message aayega whatsapp pe ya ye kya naam hai email pe jayega to aap ji kyunki aapse meri kya baat chit hui aap satisfy hai na is cheez se to aap sir ko matlab review kar dijiyega theek hai sir feedback dijiye apna.
Customer: Bas bas.
Executive: Okay sir thank you sir.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer received a call from Mr. Prince.

- Catalog was allegedly down for two weeks.

- Rates not updated in the catalog.



Resolution:

- Executive clarified he is Mr. Prince Choudhary.

- Explained calls can be from mobile/virtual numbers.

- Customer confirmed receiving inquiries.

- Executive offered to share a video meet link.

- Executive confirmed the customer is active.

- Executive will close the ticket.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will call back later.

- Customer to save executive's number.

- Customer to provide feedback on WhatsApp/email.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- catalog, inquiries, account manager, ticket
